# Don't ship anything build-time — the Dockerfile reinstalls deps and rebuilds.
# Excluding node_modules also avoids transient "invalid file request" failures
# when pnpm's symlink farm shifts under us mid-context-transfer.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/.cache
**/.vite
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Local-only config and state
.env
.env.local
.git
.github
.claude
.data
backups
handoff
ARCHITECT-BRIEF.md
BUILD-LOG.md
REVIEW-REQUEST.md
REVIEW-FEEDBACK.md
SESSION-CHECKPOINT.md

# Editor / OS junk
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
